import { combineReducers } from '@reduxjs/toolkit'
import username from './username'
import fullname from './fullname'
import email from './email'
import thumbnailurl from './thumbnailurl'

export default combineReducers({
  username,
  fullname,
  email,
  thumbnailurl,
})
